          "process_md": "> **Registration Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Visit the [Registration page](https://medhasoft.bih.nic.in/SnatakStudent/(S(g3mz4xgoeranmfbzt31lazfp))/Register.aspx).\n**Step 2:** Enter all the mandatory details and create a new password. Validate the Captcha code.\n**Step 3:** Click on “Submit” to generate the login ID and Password.\n> **Application Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Visit the [Login page](https://medhasoft.bih.nic.in/SnatakStudent/(S(segtokfpkf2xy1vikgkqwhqx))/Login.aspx?Id=19).\n**Step 2:** Enter all the mandatory details and upload all the required documents.\n**Step 3:** Recheck all entries before final submission, no modifications can be made in the application after final submission.\n**Step 4:** Click on “Submit” and take a printout of a copy of the submitted application.\n> **Check application Details:** [Click Here.](https://medhasoft.bih.nic.in/SnatakStudent/(S(ibr5z42hxfxjsvsvthsdu5rm))/ApplicationStatusofStudent.aspx)\n\n> **Payment Done Information:** [Click Here.](https://medhasoft.bih.nic.in/SnatakStudent/(S(ibr5z42hxfxjsvsvthsdu5rm))/RPT/PaymentDoneInfo.aspx)\n\n<br>\n\n> ***Helpdesk:*** \n\nFor technical problems: [Click Here](https://medhasoft.bih.nic.in/SnatakStudent/(S(hrbnlrdjhi3044o1rrfpc4n4))/HelpDesk.aspx).\n> ***Note:*** If the name of the concerned college is not in the list, the applicant should contact the Registrar of their University and request to add its name.\n\n"
        }
